                          info.piwai.funkyjfunctional.festassert.FunkyIterableAssert<T>

public class FunkyIterableAssert<T>
extends org.fest.assertions.IteratorAssert

Assertion that enables asserting conditions on all elements of an iterable. Usage: call assertThat(Iterable) to create a new FunkyIterableAssert instance, and then call one of the available instance methods with a Condition parameter.

Author:
Pierre-Yves Ricau (py.ricau at gmail.com)
